WEBVTT

00:02:28.515 --> 00:02:32.896
bu isi ruru unyi, gbakwara oto a kpaghari


00:02:32.920 --> 00:02:35.163
na-agbata anyi n'obi

00:02:35.187 --> 00:02:37.963
mgbe o bula ekwuru 'mental.'

00:02:39.074 --> 00:02:40.774
Anyi maara onye ara ahu nke oma.

00:02:40.774 --> 00:02:43.090
Nne na nna anyi doro anyi aka na nti 
gbasara ya.

00:02:43.090 --> 00:02:45.153
"Nne,nne, gini mere 
o jikwa buru onye ara?"

00:02:45.153 --> 00:02:46.655
o bu "ogwu na-aba n'isi!


00:02:46.895 --> 00:02:49.434
ilegodu y'anya,ihe mere ya, emee gi."


00:02:49.544 --> 00:02:50.697
(Ochi)

00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:53.045
Oria oyi yaa gi,

00:02:53.069 --> 00:02:55.601
nne gi ga-ebuze gi n'ulo ogwu

00:02:55.625 --> 00:02:57.007
k'agwoo gi.

00:02:58.090 --> 00:03:00.706
Mana kwuo na i naghi eche uche nke oma,